skdetail:
Flash Briefing Skill
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
des:
The Health & Fitness Fact of The Day powered by 20 Minute Fitness is a super quick show that airs three times a week. Each episode focuses on a health & fitness fact, advice or even debunks some common myths in just under 5 minutes. That way you can get your daily dose of health & fitness and learn something new even before leaving the house.

The information in this skill is provided for informational and educational purposes only.
